(10, 1, '2016-04-19 11:29:56', '2016-04-19 10:29:56', 'An invitation to a fancy dress party is always going to be one to accept. A night of fun and frivolity as well as the opportunity to don the costume of your favourite character.\r\n\r\nIf you have a fancy dress night fast approaching and you\'re not sure what to wear, here are the top 10 ideas.<!--more-->\r\n<h2><strong>10. Pirate</strong></h2>\r\nChannel your inner Jack Sparrow , Long John Silver or even Adam Ant with a dandy looking <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Pirate-Costumes/Bucanneer-Pirate-Fancy-Dress-Costume\">pirate costume</a>. Instantly recognisable, <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Fancy-Dress\">cheap fancy dress</a> and perfect for men or women, it\'s a great way to combine a cool <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Pirate-Costumes/Black-Pirate-Tricorn-Hat-With-Studs-x3\">tricorn hat,</a> stripes, lace-covered blouse and thigh high boots.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-13\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/bf2654bba01b9bcf6f16dc287d45bba9.image_.306x550-167x300.jpg\" alt=\"bf2654bba01b9bcf6f16dc287d45bba9.image.306x550\" width=\"167\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h2><strong>9. Cowboy</strong></h2>\r\nIt will be a rootin\' tootin\' night when you decide to dress as a <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Wild-West-Costumes/Big-Bad-John-Cowboy-Fancy-Dress-Costumes\">cowboy</a>. Be either the good guy as the town Sheriff or the pantomime villain as you ride on in to the party with your ankle spurs tapping and your big chaps swaying in the breeze.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-14\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sm31080-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"sm31080\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h2><strong>8. Nurse</strong></h2>\r\nYou\'ll have everyone wanting you to tuck them up when you arrive dressed as a <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Accident-Emergency-Costumes/Naughty-Nurse-Female-Fancy-Dress-Costumes\">naughty nurse </a>at the party. Temperatures will rise so you\'d better have a thermometer at the ready. Your bed side manners will be praised but be ready for emergency cases where you need to mop the occasional fevered brow.<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-15\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sm24477-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"sm24477\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h2><strong>7. Elvis\r\n</strong></h2>\r\nIt will be a night of Viva Las Vegas which will leave everyone All Shook Up when you arrive looking just like <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Licensed-Elvis-Costumes/Officially-Licensed-Black-Elvis-male-Fancy-Dress-Costumes\">Elvis</a>. Wear your best Blue Suede Shoes to dance the night away and have a comb ready to keep your quiffed wig looking perfect.  <strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-16\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sm29150-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"sm29150\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h2><strong>6. Marilyn Monroe</strong></h2>\r\nIf your party piece is to sing Happy Birthday Mr President or all you want to do is dress up as one of the most famous women in the world ever, it\'s time to bouffant your <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Licensed-Marilyn-Costumes/Officially-Licensed-Marilyn-Monroe-Blonde-Wigs\">blonde wig</a> and to step into the iconic white dress to become <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Licensed-Marilyn-Costumes/Officially-Licensed-Marilyn-Monroe-Classic-Fancy-Dress-Costumes\">Marilyn Monroe</a>. Just add  pair of white high heeled shoes and pout your lips as you apply the bright red lipstick and you\'re ready.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-17\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sm27428-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"sm27428\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h2><strong>5. Superhero</strong></h2>\r\nLet your imagination run wild and dress up as a superhero. It\'s tights, underpants and capes all the way to recreate your childhood cartoon favourite and if you fly in as <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Superhero-Costumes/Deluxe-Superman-Adult-Costume\">Superman </a>you\'ll soon have a Lois Lane by your side. Flex your muscles and gel back your hair, it\'s time to party.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-18\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/ru17963-164x300.jpg\" alt=\"ru17963\" width=\"164\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h2><strong>4. Animal</strong></h2>\r\nGreat for winter parties when warmth takes precedence over skimpy or you want to be able to hide beneath a furry mask and prowl around the dance floor, dressing up as an <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Party-Animals-Costumes/Deluxe-Chicken-Fancy-Dress-Costumes\">animal </a>is a great way to relax and look cool for cats. Being a party animal has never been so much fun and you even get to swing your tail in time to the disco tunes being played.<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-19\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sm25503-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"sm25503\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h2><strong>3. Grease</strong></h2>\r\nDress up as Sandy, <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Licensed-Grease-Costumes/Officially-Licensed-T-Bird-Jacket-With-Embroidered-Logo\">Danny</a> or one of the <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Licensed-Grease-Costumes/Officially-Licensed-Pink-Ladies-Jackets\">Pink Ladies</a> from Grease and you won\'t ever be told that you Gotta Shape Up. You\'ll be recognised as fast as Grease Lightening and you\'ll be so recognisable you won\'t need to say Look at Me, I\'m <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Licensed-Grease-Costumes/Officially-Licensed-Sandy-Female-Costumes\">Sandra Dee</a> with the fantastic 50s rock and roll look which made the film so famous.<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-20\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sm28385-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"sm28385\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h2><strong>2. Disco Fever</strong></h2>\r\nStep into your Cuban heels, pop on the flares, add big shades and clashing colours and you\'ll be certainly Staying Alive when you hit the dance floor with your disco moves. Whether you\'re a <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/70s-Disco-Fever-Costumes/1970s-Super-Trooper-Costume\">Super Trooper</a> or a Top of the Pops <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/70s-Disco-Fever-Costumes/70s-Diva-Female-Fancy-Dress-Costumes\">diva</a> , you\'ll certainly look groovy as you wow with your Retro Hustle, The Bump and end the night with a glorious rendition of Y.M.C.A.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-21\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sm33483-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"sm33483\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h2><strong>1. Ye Olde England</strong></h2>\r\nWhether you\'ve always dreamed about being <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Tales-Of-Old-England-Costumes/Maid-Marion-Fancy-Dress-Costumes-Medium-Size-Only\">Maid Marian</a> being rescued from the clutches of the  evil <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Tales-Of-Old-England-Costumes/Sheriff-Of-Nottingham-Male-Fancy-Dress-Costumes\">Sheriff of Nottingham</a> or a dashing <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Tales-Of-Old-England-Costumes/Robin-Hood-Male-Fancy-Dress-Costumes\">Robin Hood</a> coming to the rescue, there\'s lots of great way to dress up for a fancy dress party which has a Medieval England theme. Just turn up with a flagon of mead for the host and you\'ll have the best night of your life.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-22\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sm36155-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"sm36155\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />', 'Top 10 Fancy Dress Ideas', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'top-10-fancy-dress-ideas', '', '', '2018-11-14 08:19:56', '2018-11-14 08:19:56', '', 0, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?p=10', 0, 'post', '', 0),
