(29, 1, '2016-05-11 16:44:02', '2016-05-11 15:44:02', 'There is something about the word wedding that suddenly increases the value of something very quickly. That is why going to a <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/\"><strong>wholesale party supplies</strong></a> company can help reduce a budget while making maximum impact for you and your guests.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nWhen it comes to decorating a venue it is usually something which is placed at the bottom of the priority pile and delegated to family members, overseen by the bride when she has time. With the increase in package weddings, decorating a venue is not something that necessarily needs a great deal of thought from the bride and groom as most packages will have specially designed venues which will fit any colour scheme. If however you are organising the wedding venue yourself, it is important to think carefully about how to get the best from your money and how to create the atmosphere that you would like.\r\n<h2><u>Wedding Colours</u></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Find <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/\"><strong>wholesale party supplies</strong></a> that suit your colour scheme or decorations which offer a neutral effect. This will give maximum impact and tie both the colours that you love for your wedding in perfectly with the decorations. We actually have our own <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Wedding-By-Colour\">wedding by colour</a> filter options to help with this.</li>\r\n 	<li>Think about the existing colours of the room and how this will work with your own colour scheme. You may find yourself being inventive if your room is a complete contrast to your colour scheme.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><u>Decorations</u></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-30\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/pexels-photo-10.jpg\" alt=\"pexels-photo (10)\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Choose decorations carefully. More often than not, less is more but there is a fine line between too much and not enough, leaving a room looking bare and stark.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Wedding-Balloons\">Wedding balloons</a> are a staple essential at a wedding and so it goes without saying that these can be bought much cheaper when bought wholesale.</li>\r\n 	<li>Think about the decorations style. Although you may have considered what decorations you are going to have in your room, have you thought about how they will go? Drapes, material and ribbons can all be bought cheaply, especially from a wholesale party supplier and a small amount of material can go a long way, giving a little lift to a plain room.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><u>Outdoor weddings</u></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Sky-Lanterns-and-Balloon-Nets\">Sky lanterns</a> can make a superb effect when released in the dark, really setting the scene for a newlywed couple. There is something quite enchanting about watching them float off into the air.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-31\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/pexels-photo-31248.jpg\" alt=\"pexels-photo-31248\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />\r\n<h2><u>Table decorations</u></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Don’t neglect those little touches that make everything special, such as favours or sparkly <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Wedding-Table-Diamantes\">wedding table decorations</a>.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Sky-Lanterns/Heart-Candle-Bags-x-10?cPath=886_952&amp;\">Paper candle bags</a> can look beautiful on tables, especially when the lights are low. They also make beautiful walkway lighting. Flame retardant and offering a gentle glow, they really do make a stunning backdrop for a night to remember.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Place-Cards\">Place cards</a> are often neglected but it is always something that guests will notice. This is a really nice way to tie extra colour into your tables as place cards are usually cream or white. We have a really good choice of colours and themes which will tie into almost any wedding.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhile we are on about cost and buying wedding supplies in bulk, it makes sense to buy everything from a single party wholesale company, preferably in bulk as most things will work out more efficient in cost when bought from a company that offers wholesale party supplies. We do have a large choice and would be delighted to answer any questions you may have regarding wholesale party supplies so please do get in contact with us <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Contact-Us\">here</a> or call 01438 745746.', '9 Ways to decorate a wedding venue on a budget', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '9-ways-to-decorate-a-wedding-venue-on-a-budget', '', '', '2018-11-14 08:19:05', '2018-11-14 08:19:05', '', 0, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?p=29', 0, 'post', '', 0),
