(32, 1, '2016-05-11 16:43:50', '2016-05-11 15:43:50', 'There is something about the word wedding that suddenly increases the value of something very quickly. That is why going to a <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/\"><strong>wholesale party supplies</strong></a> company can help reduce a budget while making maximum impact for you and your guests.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nWhen it comes to decorating a venue it is usually something which is placed at the bottom of the priority pile and delegated to family members, overseen by the bride when she has time. With the increase in package weddings, decorating a venue is not something that necessarily needs a great deal of thought from the bride and groom as most packages will have specially designed venues which will fit any colour scheme. If however you are organising the wedding venue yourself, it is important to think carefully about how to get the best from your money and how to create the atmosphere that you would like.\r\n<h2><u>Wedding Colours</u></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Find <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/\"><strong>wholesale party supplies</strong></a> that suit your colour scheme or decorations which offer a neutral effect. This will give maximum impact and tie both the colours that you love for your wedding in perfectly with the decorations. We actually have our own <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Wedding-By-Colour\">wedding by colour</a> filter options to help with this.</li>\r\n 	<li>Think about the existing colours of the room and how this will work with your own colour scheme. You may find yourself being inventive if your room is a complete contrast to your colour scheme.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><u>Decorations</u></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-30\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/pexels-photo-10.jpg\" alt=\"pexels-photo (10)\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Choose decorations carefully. More often than not, less is more but there is a fine line between too much and not enough, leaving a room looking bare and stark.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Wedding-Balloons\">Wedding balloons</a> are a staple essential at a wedding and so it goes without saying that these can be bought much cheaper when bought wholesale.</li>\r\n 	<li>Think about the decorations style. Although you may have considered what decorations you are going to have in your room, have you thought about how they will go? Drapes, material and ribbons can all be bought cheaply, especially from a wholesale party supplier and a small amount of material can go a long way, giving a little lift to a plain room.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><u>Outdoor weddings</u></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Sky-Lanterns-and-Balloon-Nets\">Sky lanterns</a> can make a superb effect when released in the dark, really setting the scene for a newlywed couple. There is something quite enchanting about watching them float off into the air.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-31\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/pexels-photo-31248.jpg\" alt=\"pexels-photo-31248\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />\r\n<h2><u>Table decorations</u></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Don’t neglect those little touches that make everything special, such as favours or sparkly <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Wedding-Table-Diamantes\">wedding table decorations</a>.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Sky-Lanterns/Heart-Candle-Bags-x-10?cPath=886_952&amp;\">Paper candle bags</a> can look beautiful on tables, especially when the lights are low. They also make beautiful walkway lighting. Flame retardant and offering a gentle glow, they really do make a stunning backdrop for a night to remember.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Place-Cards\">Place cards</a> are often neglected but it is always something that guests will notice. This is a really nice way to tie extra colour into your tables as place cards are usually cream or white. We have a really good choice of colours and themes which will tie into almost any wedding.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhile we are on about cost and buying wedding supplies in bulk, it makes sense to buy everything from a single party wholesale company, preferably in bulk as most things will work out more efficient in cost when bought from a company that offers wholesale party supplies. We do have a large choice and would be delighted to answer any questions you may have regarding wholesale party supplies so please do get in contact with us <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Contact-Us\">here</a> or call 01438 745746.', '9 Ways to decorate a wedding venue on a budget', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-11 16:43:50', '2016-05-11 15:43:50', '', 29, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/2016/05/11/29-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(34, 1, '2016-05-16 12:45:11', '2016-05-16 11:45:11', 'On April 21th 2016, the Queen will have reached the grand age of 90 and that makes her something of a legend. She is the longest reigning monarch in history and we actually think she is pretty cool. Following on from the popularity of the street parties that arrived on her Jubilee, we think everyone should follow the trend and celebrate her official birthday on Saturday June 11<sup>th</sup> by hosting another street party.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nThe thing is about street parties is they are super cheap to organise and they bring whole groups of people together from different cultures, backgrounds and often races to all celebrate a single cause. The monarch, so in true British style we have a selection of street <strong>party wholesale</strong> decorations that will suit the cause perfectly because there is nothing more we love than being British. In fact we have a whole section dedicated to <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Best-Of-British\">The Best of British</a> – Because that’s how we roll.\r\n\r\nGet it organised, ask everyone on your street to make their favourite dish, bake cakes or make up sandwiches, everyone chips in a pound to pay for supplies and away you go.\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Best-Of-British-Tableware\">British Tableware</a></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-35\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/british-tea-party.png\" alt=\"british tea party\" width=\"500\" height=\"497\" />\r\n\r\nNow while we do appreciate that the chances of finding 10 or so tables that are all the same height on one street is slim, there is no reason to neglect table decorations. We literally have everything from napkins, party boxes, plates, cups and cutlery. Plus we are also able to offer all of our tableware at <strong>wholesale party</strong> prices. And we even have <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Best-Of-British-Tableware/Great-Britain-Union-Jack-Flag-Umbrellas-x20\">umbrellas</a> because although we love to let the world know we’re British, chances are it will rain at some point throughout the day. (We are only messing, these are for drinks)\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Best-Of-British-Party-Decorations\">Street party decorations</a></h2>\r\nWhat we love more than a good bash is <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Best-Of-British-Party-Decorations\">British street party decorations</a>. Just like tableware, these can be bought at <strong>wholesale party</strong> prices when bought in bulk, meaning that every available space can be be-decked in British flags, streamers and bunting, giving a real ‘We love Britain’ feel.\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Balloons</span></h2>\r\nNo party is complete without balloons. We just can’t get enough of them. In fact there is always an excuse for balloons, so the Queens 90<sup>th</sup> Birthday is an excellent celebration for us to get those <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Age-90-Balloons\">happy 90 Birthday balloons</a> out and wish her Happy Birthday in style. If you are feeling really creative and have lungs that are like Superman’s then you could always have 90 balloons spread around. If you manage this amount we would love a picture for our <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GoInternationalUKPartyandBalloonWholesaler/\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gointuk\">Twitter</a> pages.\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Indoor parties</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-37\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/hands-summer-party-colorful.jpg\" alt=\"hands-summer-party-colorful\" width=\"500\" height=\"344\" />\r\n\r\nIf you just do not trust the British weather then it is always handy to have somewhere indoors to go into. A village or community hall is perfect for this and the added benefit of this is that your sandwiches will not get soggy from an unexpected downpour. Our suggested street decorations work great indoors as well and can really turn a dull and drab community hall into somewhere really special without getting soaked through to the skin. While we do appreciate it is June and the weather should be kind to you, we do not need reminding that certain parts of the country received snow in April and so we just cannot rely on Mr. Weatherman to get it right.\r\n\r\nHappy Birthday to the Queen. We love being British!', 'Happy Birthday Ma’am', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'happy-birthday-maam', '', '', '2018-11-14 08:18:48', '2018-11-14 08:18:48', '', 0, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?p=34', 0, 'post', '', 0),
