(47, 1, '2016-06-15 16:01:07', '2016-06-15 15:01:07', 'More hen and stag parties are choosing to go away for the weekend for that last night of freedom. Long gone are the days when a couple of glasses of wine down the local were enough to sustain the appetites of hens who want to party. These days the bigger the party, the better. Every weekend hens are hitting towns and cities across the country clad in hen party sashes, boppers and bride L plates to enjoy a night out like no other. So here we have 4 of the best hen party venues in the UK.<!--more-->\r\n<h2><u>London</u></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-48\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/pexels-photo-50632.jpeg\" alt=\"pexels-photo-50632\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />\r\n\r\nTop on our list is our capital city. London has always been the city of choice for many southern based hens but now due to increase in cheaper train tickets, northern girls are now choosing to embark on the journey to this beautiful city. London has something for everyone. It is literally a playground to suit every hen with historical architecture, museums, shopping, markets and lastly some of the best clubs and bars in the country. What’s more, it’s a very diverse city where pretty much anything goes and as such you can really go to town with what you wear. We have an awesome selection of <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Fancy-Dress\">fancy dress costumes</a> that would suit a top night out in London, so choose the theme and away you go.\r\n<h2><u>Edinburgh</u></h2>\r\nEdinburgh is steeped in noble history, beautiful buildings, cobbled streets and steps (watch those heels). It is a city that is also renowned for being a lot cheaper than some of the cities based in the south so is ideal for the girls who want a budget friendly night out. Certain streets in Edinburgh are literally lined with bars so it really is a case of choosing where you want to head. For a night out in this beautiful city we suggest some attire that is a little more chic and sophisticated such as our <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Adult-Novelties-And-Hen-Night/Hen-Night-Dress-Up/Hen-Party-Sash2\">hen party sashes</a>. These sashes get the point across perfectly without being too OTT.\r\n<h2><u>Brighton</u></h2>\r\nSimply put Brighton is an awesome choice for hens. This bohemian city is crammed full of eccentric bars and clubs and anything will go. Although on the surface it looks like a sleepy little place during the day, once night fall comes it turns into something quite far removed from what you would expect. Plus it has a beach – you never know, the sun might just come out enough to catch a few rays sunbathing. For a top night out in Brighton we think <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Hen-Night-Dress-Up/Pink-Fairy-Wings\">pink fairy wings</a> and <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Hen-Night-Dress-Up/Pink-Hen-Party-Warning-Boppers\">boppers</a> would go down a storm and for the bride we have a full <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Hen-Night-Dress-Up/Bride-to-Be-Hen-Party-Kit\">bride-to-be set</a> that we are sure she would love!\r\n<h2><u>Blackpool</u></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-49\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/3030497272_31e1e423c9_b.jpg\" alt=\"3030497272_31e1e423c9_b\" width=\"640\" height=\"435\" />\r\n\r\nNow Blackpool has got a bit of a reputation for being THE place to go for a hen night. The attraction of a sea-side resort offers alternative day activities, especially as it is home to the Blackpool Tower and the Blackpool Pleasure Beach. What we love about Blackpool is its laid back charm. The bars and clubs are fully accommodating of hen and stag parties and as a result will welcome you in with open arms, especially when dressed up. We suggest our awesome selection of <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Fever-Burlesque-Costumes\">Fever Burlesque fancy dress</a> for a night in Blackpool – What’s more is that we can offer wholesale party prices on them for large orders, so no matter how many guests you have, we can always give the best prices.\r\n\r\nWherever you choose to go make it fun and make if affordable. <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/\">For more <strong>wholesale party supplies</strong>, please check out the rest of our website</a>. We are sure we will have something for you.', 'The 4 Best British Hen Party Venues', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-4-best-british-hen-party-venues', '', '', '2018-11-14 08:18:21', '2018-11-14 08:18:21', '', 0, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?p=47', 0, 'post', '', 0),
