n this beautiful city we suggest some attire that is a little more chic and sophisticated such as our <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Adult-Novelties-And-Hen-Night/Hen-Night-Dress-Up/Hen-Party-Sash2\">hen party sashes</a>. These sashes get the point across perfectly without being too OTT.\r\n<h2><u>Brighton</u></h2>\r\nSimply put Brighton is an awesome choice for hens. This bohemian city is crammed full of eccentric bars and clubs and anything will go. Although on the surface it looks like a sleepy little place during the day, once night fall comes it turns into something quite far removed from what you would expect. Plus it has a beach – you never know, the sun might just come out enough to catch a few rays sunbathing. For a top night out in Brighton we think <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Hen-Night-Dress-Up/Pink-Fairy-Wings\">pink fairy wings</a> and <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Hen-Night-Dress-Up/Pink-Hen-Party-Warning-Boppers\">boppers</a> would go down a storm and for the bride we have a full <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Hen-Night-Dress-Up/Bride-to-Be-Hen-Party-Kit\">bride-to-be set</a> that we are sure she would love!\r\n<h2><u>Blackpool</u></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-49\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/3030497272_31e1e423c9_b.jpg\" alt=\"3030497272_31e1e423c9_b\" width=\"640\" height=\"435\" />\r\n\r\nNow Blackpool has got a bit of a reputation for being THE place to go for a hen night. The attraction of a sea-side resort offers alternative day activities, especially as it is home to the Blackpool Tower and the Blackpool Pleasure Beach. What we love about Blackpool is its laid back charm. The bars and clubs are fully accommodating of hen and stag parties and as a result will welcome you in with open arms, especially when dressed up. We suggest our awesome selection of <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Fever-Burlesque-Costumes\">Fever Burlesque fancy dress</a> for a night in Blackpool – What’s more is that we can offer wholesale party prices on them for large orders, so no matter how many guests you have, we can always give the best prices.\r\n\r\nWherever you choose to go make it fun and make if affordable. <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/\">For more <strong>wholesale party supplies</strong>, please check out the rest of our website</a>. We are sure we will have something for you.', 'The 4 Best British Hen Party Venues', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '47-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 16:44:26', '2016-06-29 15:44:26', '', 47, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/2016/06/29/47-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(51, 1, '2016-07-01 15:54:02', '2016-07-01 14:54:02', 'They say that hitting the big 40 is the new 20. For years the 40<sup>th</sup> birthday was always seen as a benchmark age, one where you would consider that you are halfway through your life now and would hear remarks from well-meaning friends that ‘it’s all downhill from here’. Not anymore. Reaching 40 is all about knowing who you are and exactly what you want. So why not celebrate in style!\r\n\r\nFor some, the thought of throwing a big party is quite a daunting thought but thankfully we are on hand to help out with our large range of party supplies.<!--more-->\r\n<h2><u>Balloons</u></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/balls-1284418_640.jpg\" alt=\"balls-1284418_640\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />\r\n\r\nIt doesn’t matter if you are 4 or 40, everyone loves birthday balloons. There is something quite appealing and childish about bouncing a balloon around the room and watching as it gracefully falls to the floor. If it’s something we do well, it is balloons as we have so many of them! From <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Plain-Retail-Latex\">plain balloons</a> in every colour imaginable to <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Plain-Heart-Foils\">foil balloons</a>, we literally have something that will put a smile on every face. To let everyone know how old you are, why not some <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Age-40-Balloons\">40<sup>th</sup> Birthday balloons</a> as well.\r\n<h2><u>Birthday decoration</u></h2>\r\nNow we appreciate that room decorations depend on the venue, mainly whether you are celebrating indoors or outdoors but we do have one of the largest selections of party decorations in the country, so we are pretty sure we can find you something. So whether you are throwing a <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Hollywood-Decorations\">Hollywood themed birthday party</a>, a <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Adult-Fancy-Dress\">fancy dress party</a> or a simpler one we have it covered.\r\n<h2><u>Table decoration</u></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-45\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/richardmccormick_1388582407_54.jpg\" alt=\"richardmccormick_1388582407_54\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />\r\n\r\nWhen throwing a birthday party it is important to remember that your guests need somewhere to sit. Not everyone will be able to party hard and stay on their feet all night. Table decorations are a lovely way of jazzing up a boring table that may otherwise look a little bit lost in a larger room or garden. Our table decorations can be bought at wholesale party prices for the larger party as well. <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Banquet-Rolls\">Coloured banquet rolls</a> work brilliantly on longer tables while <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Balloon-Weights\">weighted bottom balloons</a> look pretty and make a lovely table centre piece.\r\n<h2><u>Food</u></h2>\r\nEveryone loves party food and for ease at a big party food usually comes in the form of a buffet style eating experience. It depends entirely on your budget and the help available as to whether you do the food yourself. Alternatively many people are choosing to get outside caterers in to do it but what we do know if we have some pretty cool tableware that will allow you guests to eat in comfort - After all, eating with your hands is a bit pre-historic. Check out our <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Plain-Paper-Tableware-Sets\">coloured tableware</a> that come in a variety of colours to perfectly match your colour theme.\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Colpac-Boxes-And-Loot-Bags\">Party bags</a></span></h2>\r\nWe don’t care how old we are, party bags will always go down a storm. They bring back memories of children’s parties, sweets and too much cake, so what better way of thanking your guests for coming then providing them with a party bag to go home with. We have a selection of party and loot bags on offer from plain coloured ones to themed ones. The least you can do is give your guests some cake to go home with. Everyone loves cake don’t they?', 'How to throw the best 40th birthday party', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-01 15:54:02', '2016-07-01 14:54:02', '', 41, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/2016/07/01/41-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(53, 1, '2016-07-19 09:53:08', '2016-07-19 08:53:08', 'Have you got a party to organise? Perhaps you have a birthday coming up? How about having a themed party? Themes can vary from really extravagant by asking your guests to dress up or as simple as just having a specific colour. We know how expensive and stressful organising a party can be but with our huge selection of <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/\">wholesale party supplies</a> we can help reduce the prices considerably and take some of the stress away. Take a look at some of our favourite ideas for creating a party to remember.<!--more-->\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Oktoberfest-Party-Supplies\">Oktoberfest Party</a></h2>\r\nFor those of you who haven’t heard of Oktoberfest, it’s an annual festival held in, yes you’ve guessed it, October! The idea is to get your guests dressed up in traditional German costumes and drink beer. We have a great selection of costumes suitable for this purpose but our favourites are these <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Around-The-World-Costumes/Girls-Tavern-Costume?cPath=2_2005&amp;\">Girls Tavern costume</a> and for the boys this <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Around-The-World-Costumes/Oktoberfest-Male-Fancy-Dress-Costumes?cPath=2_2005&amp;\">Oktoberfest costume</a>. For the decorations we have a great selection of blue and white coloured table decorations which will really get the mood sorted.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-55\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/sm20610.jpg\" alt=\"sm20610\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Best-Of-British\">A Really British Bash</a></h2>\r\nWhat with celebrating the Queens 90<sup>th</sup> birthday this year, the Rio Olympics on the way and Euro 2016, street parties are an ongoing trend with 1000’s of us throwing an old fashioned street party. With our wholesale party supplies throwing a British street party can actually be more affordable than you may think it would be and it’s a great excuse to get communities together. Nothing says British more than homemade cakes, sausage rolls and cookies and what better way to show them off than on one of these <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Best-Of-British-Tableware/Great-Britain-Cupcake-Stand\">Great British Cupcake Stands</a>. Get some of these <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Best-Of-British-Party-Decorations/Great-Britain-Lantern-Garlands\">British Garland Lanterns</a> and some <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Best-Of-British-Party-Decorations/Union-Jack-PVC-Flag-Bunting\">PVC bunting</a> (They won’t melt in the rain) across the street, set up some tables and there you have it, a perfect day for the kids and an even better one for getting the adults all together. Makes us proud to be British.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-56\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/az994826.jpg\" alt=\"az994826\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Summer-Theme\">Summer Party</a></h2>\r\nWe know the British weather can never be relied upon to bring sunshine so why not throw a summer themed party instead? This great idea can be done inside or out and is really easy to organise. Simply ask your guests to wear their best summer clothes and decorate the place with our awesome range of wholesale party decorations. For those spur of the moment photo moments we have this very cool <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Scene-Setter-Photo-Prop/Double-Sided-Mermaid-And-King-Neptune-Photo-Prop?cPath=467_905_1850&amp;\">double sided photo prop</a> or a choice of <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Party-Photo-Props/Beach-Party-Photo-Props?cPath=467_905_1850&amp;\">wearable photo props</a> for some very funny picture perfect moments.\r\n\r\nThese are just our 4 favourite themed party ideas but if you have other ideas we are sure that we have something to match your perfect party theme. Plus as one of the UK’s biggest suppliers of competitively priced wholesale party supplies you can’t really go wrong with shopping at Go International.', 'Themed Party Ideas and Inspiration', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'themed-party-ideas-and-inspiration', '', '', '2018-11-14 08:17:47', '2018-11-14 08:17:47', '', 0, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?p=53', 0, 'post', '', 0),
