(67, 1, '2017-09-14 18:54:45', '2017-09-14 17:54:45', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hosting a Halloween party for kids this year? </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Struggling to conjure up some fun ideas that the kids will love?</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don’t worry we’ve got something that will do just the trick! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Halloween- themed cookies! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These cookies only take</span><b> 8-10 minutes </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">to bake and can be rustled up in less than 30 minutes. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But before you grab your apron and start baking, you’ll need to get some </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Halloween-Cookie-Cutter\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Halloween shaped cookie cutters.</span></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our pack of Halloween themed </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Halloween-Cookie-Cutter\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">cookie cutters </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">comes with 5 different shapes for:</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bat</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pumpkin</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cat</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Skull </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ghost </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once you’ve got your </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Halloween-Cookie-Cutter\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">cookie cutters,</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> collect the following ingredients: </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For the cookies, you’ll need: </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">100g of caster sugar</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">100g of unsalted butter</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">275g flour</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 free-range egg</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 teaspoon of vanilla extract</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To decorate the cookies, you’ll need: </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Black and orange food colouring</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">400 grams of icing sugar </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3-4 teaspoons of water </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Also before you start, make sure that you have a sheet of greaseproof paper, a rolling pin, a wire rack and oven gloves. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Method</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Begin by firstly preheating the oven to 190C, then line a baking tray with some greaseproof paper. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Leave the butter at room temperature to soften, then combine it with the sugar in a bowl. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Add in the egg and the vanilla extract and combine well</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sift the flour, then slowly add it to the mixture and combine until dough forms. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Using the rolling pin, roll out the dough on a flat cold surface until the thickness is about 1cm. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With our five </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Halloween-Cookie-Cutter\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">cookie cutters,</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> carefully cut the cookies out of the dough, and place them onto the greaseproof paper on the baking tray. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bake the cookies for 8-10 minutes until they are lightly golden. Then carefully remove them from the oven with oven gloves. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Leave the cookies to cool on a wire rack for about 5 minutes. </span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Then to decorate the cookies: </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Add 2-3 teaspoons of water to the sifted icing sugar and combine well until you get your desired consistency. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Separate the mixture into two separate bowls. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In one bowl add the black food colouring, and in the second add the orange food coloring and stir.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Carefully spread the icing over the cookies evenly, then set aside to harden. </span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If however, you’ll be getting these cookies made, here are some tips for presenting the cookies on the day of the party: </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Serve the cookies by arranging them on a </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Foil-Trays/14-inch-Black-Foil-Platter-x1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">black platter</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and place them on the buffet table. Alternatively, you could wrap each cookie in clear cellophane wrap for each child to take home in their </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers/Spooky-Boots-Cello-Bags-x20\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">party bag</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So here we have it, Halloween themed cookie ideas that the kids will love! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you need any more ideas for treats, to compliment these cookies, you could also bake some spooky Halloween cupcakes. Our </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers/Halloween-Cupcake-Decorating-Kit\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">cupcake decorating kit</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> includes orange and black cupcake cases and Halloween flag picks. To serve the cupcakes, be sure to get one of our </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Fangtastic-Halloween-Cake-Stand\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Halloween themed cupcake </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">stands to arrange them on! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Be sure to follow us on Twitter </span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gointuk\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">@gointuk</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for business tips, party ideas and much more! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '5 Awesome Halloween-Themed Cookie Ideas The Kids Will Love', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '65-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-09-14 18:54:45', '2017-09-14 17:54:45', '', 65, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/2017/09/14/65-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(68, 1, '2017-09-22 09:30:21', '2017-09-22 08:30:21', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The leaves are turning, and the pumpkins are ripening...</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">...Halloween is</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> fast approaching,</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and it’s time to start planning for your upcoming Halloween parties!  </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Need some inspiration? Balloons are a great way to decorate your party venues -  especially when they perfectly tie into the theme of the occasion.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Luckily for you, we’ve compiled a list of 11 Halloween themed balloons that will add some eeriness to your party! </span>\r\n<h2><b>#1 Little Bat Foil Balloon</b></h2>\r\nWe’ll start right off the bat with this awesome little<a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foils/Little-Bat-Foil-Balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> bat foil balloon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-70\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/02.png\" alt=\"02\" width=\"453\" height=\"268\" />\r\n<h2><b>#2 Monster Bash Chevron Halloween Balloon</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Throwing a monster themed Halloween party for the lil’ ones? This colourful </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foils/18-inch-Monster-Bash-Chevron-halloween-helium-foil-balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">monster bash balloon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> will do just the trick!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-71\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/03.png\" alt=\"Monster Bash Balloon\" width=\"447\" height=\"449\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Top tip: Pair it with the </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foils/18-inch-Boo-Monster-Chevron-halloween-helium-foil-balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Boo monster chevron </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">balloon. Together, this dynamic duo will be sure to liven up the party atmosphere! </span>\r\n<h2><b>#3 Great Pumpkin Halloween Balloon</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pumpkins are synonymous with Halloween - so the </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foil-Balloons/18-inch-Great-Pumpkin-halloween-helium-foil-balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Great Pumpkin</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> balloon is perfect for the occasion!</span>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-72\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Pumpkin-Balloon.png\" alt=\"Pumpkin Balloon\" width=\"435\" height=\"436\" />\r\n<h2><b>#4 Boo-ya Ghosts Balloon</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Next up, we have the </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foils/18-inch-Boo-Ya-Ghosts-halloween-helium-foil-balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Boo-ya Ghosts</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> balloon - it’s sure to add some humour to your party! </span>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Boo-ya-Balloon-.png\" alt=\"Boo-ya Balloon\" width=\"473\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<h2><b>#5 Ghost Foil Balloon</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Next up, sticking with the theme of ghosts <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">here’s a </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foil-Balloons/18-inch-Cute-Ghost-halloween-helium-foil-balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">cute ghost</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> balloon with a </span><b>bright smile</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:</span></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-75\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/ghost-foil-Baloon-1.png\" alt=\"ghost foil Baloon\" width=\"431\" height=\"426\" />\r\n<h2><b>#6 Happy Ghost Balloon</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here we have a </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foil-Balloons/Happy-Ghost-Foil-Balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">happy ghost</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> balloon that is sure to bring a bubbly aura into the room!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-76\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Happy-ghost-balloon.png\" alt=\"Happy ghost balloon\" width=\"403\" height=\"454\" />\r\n<h2><b>#7 Moonlight Bat Balloon</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There is no better way to bring spookiness to the party than with this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foil-Balloons/18-inch-Moonlight-Bat-halloween-foil-balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">moonlight bat</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-77\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/bat-balloon.png\" alt=\"bat balloon\" width=\"463\" height=\"460\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Top tip: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Talking about spookiness, check out this black and white </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Decoration/Spider-Web-Cut-Out-Banner\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">spider banner</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> that will make your quiver!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-78\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/spider-banner.png\" alt=\"spider banner\" width=\"448\" height=\"462\" />\r\n<h2><b>#8 Boo Spider Balloon</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Keeping in line with the spider theme, check out this square 18-inch foil </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foil-Balloons/18-inch-BOO-Spider-halloween-helium-foil-balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">boo spider balloon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">! </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-79\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Spider-boo-balloon.png\" alt=\"Spider boo balloon\" width=\"423\" height=\"409\" />\r\n<h2><b>#9 Skeleton Boo Balloon</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Going for the traditional orange, black and white colour theme? The </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foil-Balloons/18-inch-Halloween-Skeleton-BOO-halloween-helium-foil-balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">skeleton boo</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> balloon will beautifully complement the rest of your decor.</span>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Skeleton-boo.png\" alt=\"Skeleton boo\" width=\"448\" height=\"455\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Top tip:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> if your guests will be arriving in fancy dress, why not host a competition to reward the person who turns up in the spookiest attire? Check out our </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Skeleton-Best-Costume-Trophy\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">skeleton trophy,</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> it’s the perfect prize for the worthy winner. </span>\r\n<h2><b>#10 Halloween Kitty Balloon</b></h2>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foil-Balloons/Halloween-Kitty-Cat-Foil-Balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This balloon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> features a black cat and a pumpkin! Isn’t that black kitty just so cute?!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-81\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/cat-pumpkin.png\" alt=\"cat pumpkin\" width=\"462\" height=\"460\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><b>#11 Hello Kitty Halloween Balloon</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hello, Kitty is undeniably cute, and our final balloon is no exception! Here is a lovely </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-SuperShapes/Hello-Kitty-Cat-Costume-Halloween-SuperShape-Balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hello Kitty Balloon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-82\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Hello-kitty-balloon.png\" alt=\"Hello kitty balloon\" width=\"462\" height=\"455\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So here we have it folks, 11 of the cutest Halloween balloons! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We’ll leave you with a final </span><b>top tip</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> - at the end of the party, allow your guests to take a balloon home with them, along with their party bags! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We hope your Halloween party planning goes smoothly! Be sure to check out our website for more themed balloons and </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Halloween party essentials</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">! We’ve got everything you’ll need to make your Halloween parties extra special!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One last note, here at Go International, we are in the unique position to be able to offer you helium gas canisters from both BOC and Airproducts to meet your balloon filling requirements.We also offer disposable helium gas which comes with a filling valve </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Balloon-Gas-Rental\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Read more.</span></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Also, follow us on Twitter for party planning tips and to keep up to date with our latest product releases </span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gointuk\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">@gointuk</span></a>', '11 Super Cute Halloween Balloon Designs', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '11-super-cute-halloween-balloon-designs', '', '', '2018-11-14 08:15:49', '2018-11-14 08:15:49', '', 0, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?p=68', 0, 'post', '', 0),
