(101, 1, '2017-09-27 19:32:27', '2017-09-27 18:32:27', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We don\'t know about you, but we are beyond ready for cool weather, bonfires, football and best of all Halloween! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are on the move trying to figure out the best ideas for throwing a glamorous Halloween party that your friends will be talking about all the way through Christmas!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We\'ve come up with a few tips to get you headed in the right direction.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Follow us as we teach you how to throw the best Glam-o-ween party of the season!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"># 1: Choose Your Theme</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-96\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/lanterns.jpg\" alt=\"Halloween Lanterns\" width=\"429\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The first thing you are going to need to do is to choose a theme for your party.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of our most popular party themes is the orange and black party theme. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Make sure to order a few packs of </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Decoration/Orange-Black-Halloween-Lanterns-3pk?cPath=&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">orange and black Halloween lanterns</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to give your party the soft but spooky glow it needs. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">No matter which Halloween theme you choose, you can be sure it will be glamourous if decorated the right way. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Top tip: Make sure to hang these throughout the room for maximum effect. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"># 2: Choose Your Decorations with Care</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nothing says Halloween like decorations that sizzle. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Make sure that the decorations you choose are classy but creepy at the same time. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Decoration/Haunted-House-Centrepiece?cPath=&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Haunted House Centerpiece</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> would look amazing in the middle of a dining room table, surrounded by plates and other Halloweeny decorations. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-97\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/two2.jpg\" alt=\"Halloween decor\" width=\"477\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Choose other decorations that match the theme you have chosen.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The last thing you need is a mix match, hodge podge of decorations.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Top Tip: Make sure to arrange your centerpiece where it doesn\'t get in the way of the food and tableware you set out. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"># 3: Choose Your Tableware</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether you want your tableware to be classic or Halloween inspired, we have the perfect choices. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Jet-Black-Tableware/Jet-Black-Paper-Tablecover-1pk?cPath=&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jet Black Paper Tablecloth Cover</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> can be used to hold that gorgeous centerpiece you bought. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Make sure that the tableware you choose to grace your Halloween party goes well with the theme you have planned for the perfect spooky atmosphere.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Top tip: Pair the tablecloth with our other </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Jet-Black-Tableware/Jet-Black-Paper-Plates-8pk?cPath=&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jet Black tableware</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for a haunting, eerie look your guests will love. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-98\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/three3.jpg\" alt=\"tablecloth\" width=\"458\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"># 4: Choose the Food</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You will want to choose your food with care of course. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether it\'s orange and black cupcakes or a Halloween cake for dessert, it will sit perfectly on our  </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Fangtastic-Halloween-Cake-Stand?cPath=&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fantastic Halloween Cake Stand</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-99\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/four-4.jpg\" alt=\"cake stand\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are many, many foods out there that can be turned into Halloween food. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From olives as eyeballs and finger food as fingers, the possibilities are endless. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Top tip: Make sure to serve everything on throwaway plates so cleanup is a breeze when the party is done. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, there you have it!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The perfect tips for throwing your very own glamorous Halloween party. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Remember, food, decorations, and a theme your guests can relate too are must-haves that will make your party the most talked about this Halloween season. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don\'t forget to follow us on Twitter </span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gointuk\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">@gointuk</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for all the latest in costumes and accessories for Halloween and beyond. </span>', 'Glam-o-ween: How To Throw A Glamourous Halloween Party', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '94-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-09-27 19:32:27', '2017-09-27 18:32:27', '', 94, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/2017/09/27/94-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
