(103, 1, '2017-10-01 09:30:58', '2017-10-01 08:30:58', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Halloween is the time of year where everyone can forget who they are for one night and pretend to be whoever, or whatever they want to be instead.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While adults love to dress up and hit the parties on All Hallows Eve, the holiday is in fact extremely special to the children. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you are throwing a Halloween party for the little goblins and witches in your neighborhood, then you are going to want some party bag ideas that the kids will love. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We have a list of the best items to put in those party bags to make your guests happy this Halloween season. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"># 1: The Bags</span>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/cello-1.jpg\" alt=\"cello bags\" width=\"222\" height=\"500\" /></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The proper Halloween favors call for the proper Halloween bags first and foremost. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers/Spooky-Boots-Cello-Bags-x20?cPath=&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Spooky Boots Cello Bags</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> come in a package of 20 to help you meet the needs of everyone on at your party.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These bags are pretty and spooky at the same time. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Just the trick for little ones looking for treats this Halloween. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Top tip: Make sure to tie the tops of the treat bags with orange and black ribbon so the little ones don\'t lose any of the treats inside on their way home. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"># 2: Pumpkin Headbands for the Girls</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-107\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/pump.jpg\" alt=\"pumpkin headband\" width=\"382\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For the girls at your Halloween party, our </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers/Pumpkin-Headband?cPath=&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pumpkin Headband </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is just the thing to add to their party bag. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Equip with a pumpkin on top, black wings, and even a little green stem on top, this is the perfect favor for any little witch or princess.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It\'s something that she will play with during dressup for many months to come, maybe even through Christmas. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Top tip. Since the pumpkin headband won\'t fit in the party bags you have bought, try hanging the headbands over the bags themselves. It\'s cute and spooky at the same time!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"># 3: Spooky Spider Toys for the Boys</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-108\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/spider.jpg\" alt=\"spider toys\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Instead, use this 24-pack of </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers/Spooky-Spider-Toys-24pk?cPath=&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Spooky Spider Toys</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for the boys in the group. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With this amount, you can even add two for double the fun for your Halloween guests. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Top tip: Leave some of the spider toys out for the girls, just in case they want one, you never know, some girls might.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"># 4: Zombie Nightwalker Beanies</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-109\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/beanies.jpg\" alt=\"beanies\" width=\"400\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers/6-Inch-Zombie-Nightwalker-Beanies?cPath=&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Zombie Nightwalker Beanies </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">are six inches tall and come in four different varieties so you can vary what comes in the party bags by what each child likes. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Most kids love figures and the idea of having their very own zombie beanie to carry around will appeal to most. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Zombie Beanies are the perfect complement to the other items you add to their bags.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don\'t forget the candy treats and the Halloween bubbles, so that your little guests will leave your party more than happy they came. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These are a few of the best spooky Halloween party bag ideas out there today. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Your little goblins and witches will be thrilled. </span>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Make sure to follow us on Twitter </span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gointuk\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">@gointuk</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for more Halloween specials on party bag ideas and more. </span>', '4 Spooky Halloween Party Bag Ideas The Kids Will Love', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '4-spooky-halloween-party-bag-ideas-the-kids-will-love', '', '', '2018-11-14 08:14:26', '2018-11-14 08:14:26', '', 0, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?p=103', 0, 'post', '', 0),
