(117, 1, '2017-10-02 15:13:28', '2017-10-02 14:13:28', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">October is finally here…</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">...and it’s time to get everyone together for a Halloween party!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But what’s a Halloween party without spooky fancy dress costumes? </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether you’re throwing an office party or organising a Halloween party for your clients, getting the guests to arrive in fancy dress will play a big part in the overall success of the party by adding an element of fun and creativity. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It can even inject a spirit of competitiveness, as you can incentivise your guest to dress up with a competition for the scariest costume. Our </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Skeleton-Best-Costume-Trophy\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">skeleton trophy</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is the perfect reward for the worthy winner - and for the runner-up, you could present them with a </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Search-Results?search_in_description=1&amp;keyword=halloween&amp;inc_subcat=0&amp;sort=20a&amp;page=2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">sash</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for the funniest costume!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here’s a list of accessories that are bound to add that extra bit of spookiness to any outfit:</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#1: Glow In The Dark Finger Nails</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First up are these </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Glow-In-The-Dark-Finger-Nails\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">glow in the dark fingernails</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<