(120, 1, '2017-10-08 09:30:34', '2017-10-08 08:30:34', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">...And here we are again! October has arrived and Halloween is just around the corner. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now is the perfect time to start thinking about all little details that will make your parties </span><b>extra special.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the best things about Halloween is trick-or-treating, and collecting lots of sweets of course!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">That’s why we have put together a list of 3 of our trick-or-treat baskets: </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#1: Witches’ Cauldron</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First up is the </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Halloween-Witches-Cauldron\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Witches’ Cauldron</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Its small size is perfect for the little ones to carry! </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-121\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/small-witches_cauldron.png\" alt=\"small witches cauldron\" width=\"361\" height=\"516\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Top tip:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> If you decide to have a pinata at your party, once the pinata has been smashed open and all the sweets have been released, you could hand everyone one of these baskets to gather up all the sweets off the floor!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#2: Lifesize Witches Cauldron</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Next up, we have this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/LifeSize-Witches-Cauldron\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">lifesize witches’ cauldron</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. If you are looking for a trick or treat basket that is on the larger side, this is the one for you!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-122\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/witches_cauldron_large.png\" alt=\"witches_cauldron_large\" width=\"357\" height=\"502\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Top tips:</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> If you will be providing each of your guests one of these baskets, consider putting </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Search-Results?search_in_description=1&amp;keyword=label&amp;inc_subcat=0&amp;sort=20a&amp;page=4\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">name labels</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> on them so that no one gets their basket mixed up with anyone else\'s basket!</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You could also use these large cauldrons as serving bowls! Simply fill them with sweet treats, and allow your guests to help themselves. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A fun activity would be to allow the kids to personalise their baskets with stickers! These </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Special-Events-And-Seasonal-Party-Supplies/Halloween/Halloween-Decoration/Halloween-Decoration/Halloween-Embossed-Window-Stickers\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Halloween themed stickers</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> would do just the trick!</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#3: Plastic Pumpkin Sweets Basket</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And last, but not least, we have this bright orange </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Pumpkin-Plastic-Sweet-Bucket\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">pumpkin shaped trick or treat basket</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> that is a much more manageable size for younger kids. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-123\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/pumpkin_basket.png\" alt=\"pumpkin_basket\" width=\"352\" height=\"517\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Top tips:</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alongside the more traditional party bag, filled with a selection of gruesome treats, you could also send your guests home with a basket full of sweets in one of these pumpkin-shaped baskets! </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There you have it folks, 3 trick or treat baskets! We wish you all a spooktacular Halloween season! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For our entire selection of Halloween themed supplies, </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">click here</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With over </span><b>25 years experience</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, we\'ve helped thousands of customers to </span><b>grow their business</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, which means we know which party supplies you need, and what you don\'t!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We sell a massive range of over 1 million party supplies to both wholesale and retail customers, with everything from party accessories to hen night supplies and wholesale party decorations at </span><b>great prices</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Need an </span><b>express</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> or </span><b>next day</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> delivery? We’ve got you covered! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With all that said, If you need ANY help or advice at all with your party planning, or if there is so