(157, 1, '2017-10-29 09:30:22', '2017-10-29 09:30:22', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Halloween is fast approaching! By now, you’ve probably come up with some costume ideas! Perhaps you want to dress up as a witch, or even a zombie.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But whatever you decide to go as, wearing a wig that complements your ghoulish attire can really transform your outfit. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The great things about wearing wigs are:</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They are quick and easy to fit.  </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They come pre-styled.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Are inexpensive. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Need some inspiration? </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We’ve compiled a list of 4 wig ideas to complement your Halloween costume: </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#1: Day of the Dead Wig </span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Day-of-the-dead-wig.png\" alt=\"Day of the dead wig\" width=\"450\" height=\"433\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First up on the list is this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Wigs/Day-Of-The-Dead-Wig?cPath=2_418_1561&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Day of the Dead Wig</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Its two-toned colouring and accent roses make it the perfect addition to any costume. This wig works well with a Day of the Dead costume, hence the name, but it can be used for many other costumes too! Add some face paint, and you’ll be ready to go! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Top tip:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> pair this stunning wig with our red and black Day of the Dead</span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Day-Of-The-Dead-Costumes/Day-Of-The-Dead-Bride-Costume\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> bride costume</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">! </span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#2: Gothic Bride Wig </span></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Next, we have the </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Fancy-Dress-Costumes/Halloween-Fancy-Dress/Halloween-Wigs/Deluxe-Gothic-Bride-Wig?cPath=2_418_1561&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gothic Bride Wig</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. With the grays in this one, you’re sure to spook all of your friends, regardless of the costume you’re wearing. Pair it with a white dress and some pale face makeup, and you will look like a gothic bride! Or wear it with another costume to add a bit of an old-time feel to your look!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-159\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Grey-wig.png\" alt=\"gothic bride wig\" width=\"442\" height=\"439\" />\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#3: Zombie Wig</span></h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-160\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Zombie-Wig.png\" alt=\"Zombie wig\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A zombie is one of the most classically scary Halloween choices, and it’s easy to construct this costume out of a variety of pieces. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One tip is to use this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Fancy-Dress-Costumes/Halloween-Fancy-Dress/Halloween-Wigs/Deluxe-Zombie-Blood-Drip-Wig?cPath=2_418_1561&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Blood Drip Zombie Wig</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to make your costume even more terrifying. Add some </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Fake-Blood/Fake-Blood-Clothing-Spray-75ml\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">fake blood</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to your clothing and on your face to complete the look! Perfect your zombie walk before heading out, and you’ll kill at the Halloween party!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Top tip:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in order to care and maintain your costume wigs, avoid using hairspray, gels, and other haircare products that are made for human hair. Instead, fill a spray bottle with some warm water, dampen the hair, and gently detangle with your fingertips - avoid brushing until the hair has completely air dried. </span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#4: Witch Wig</span></h1>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-161\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Witch-wig.png\" alt=\"witch wig\" width=\"428\" height=\"429\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Last but not least, we have this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Wigs/Long-Black-Witch-Wigs?cPath=2_418_1561&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Long Black Witch Wig</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. It would obviously work excellently for any witch costume, but it could also be used for many other eerie characters. Be ready to scare someone after applying some costume makeup! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Top tip:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> be sure to finish off this look with a </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Hats/Witches-Hats\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">witch hat</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So here we have it folks, 4 wig ideas to complement your Halloween Outfit!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Remember, don’t be afraid to mix and match wigs with costumes that are differently themed, too. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sometimes one piece can work for many different outfits. Here at Go International, we have a wide variety of wigs for sale, check out our full range </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Wigs\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">here</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Also, follow us on Twitter for party planning tips and to keep up to date with our latest product releases</span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gointuk\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">@gointuk</span></a>', '4 Wig Ideas to Complement Your Halloween Costume', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '4-wig-ideas-to-complement-your-halloween-costume', '', '', '2018-11-14 08:09:20', '2018-11-14 08:09:20', '', 0, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?p=157', 0, 'post', '', 0),
