(164, 1, '2017-10-27 09:30:33', '2017-10-27 08:30:33', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s time to start adding the finishing touches to your Halloween costumes! </span>\r\n\r\nCapes are a  great Halloween costume accessory, as they can really enhance your outfit, and they can also help to keep you nice and toasty!\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">luckily for you, we made it easy for you to find one final piece to bring it all together! </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here is a list of 9 spooky capes that you can add on to your Halloween costume! </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#1: Black Witches Cape </span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Capes/Deluxe-Witches-Capes\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Deluxe Black Witches Cape</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is ideal for any classic witch costume. The black color is easy to mix and match with other pieces, so you don’t have to wear it with a particular color or style. It’s very versatile! It also comes in other colors, such as teal, purple, and red. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-165\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/1-2.png\" alt=\"black witches cape\" width=\"282\" height=\"286\" />\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#2: Vampire Bat Wings</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now, this isn’t your typical cape that you would think of superheroes or witches wearing, but it still falls under the same category. These </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Capes/Vampire-Bat-Wings\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vampire Bat Wings </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">are the perfect complement to any vampire costume, any bat costume, or any combination of the two. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-166\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog