(187, 1, '2017-10-29 22:06:31', '2017-10-29 22:06:31', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Getting dressed up for a Halloween party can be hard work! Firstly, you have to pick a costume, then find some gruesome accessories to pair with it! On top of that, you might decide to finish off your look with a face of spooky makeup! </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Luckily for you, we have a wide selection of makeup kits that are perfect for Halloween! Here are 8 of them: </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#1 Skeleton Latex Kit</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First up, we have this <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Fancy-Dress-Costumes/Halloween-Fancy-Dress/Halloween-Make-Up-Kits/Skeleton-Liquid-Latex-Kit?cPath=2_418_2013&amp;\">latex skeleton kit</a>! Skeletons are a classic symbol of Halloween! It’s perfectly spooky without being over the top. To achieve the look, simply follow the 5 stages illustrated below: </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-189\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/one.png\" alt=\"makeup kit\" width=\"217\" height=\"216\" />\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#2 Glow in the Dark Skeleton Kit </span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Maybe you like the previous skeleton kit, but you want to take it a step further. How about using this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Make-Up-Kits/Glow-In-The-Dark-Skeleton-Make-Up-Kit?cPath=2_418_2013&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Glow in the Dark Skeleton Kit</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to make your costume extra creepy?</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-190\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/two.png\" alt=\"makeup kit\" width=\"134\" height=\"214\" />\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#3 Zombie Latex Kit </span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another staple