wn. Who do we turn to the good helpful advice, so what\'s the real reason people are offering us whatever they\'re offering us is it and what\'s in it for me scenario which regrettably most of times it is or are they actually looking at helping us grow. Again I\'m gonna go back to NABAS. Although I\'m kind of really promoting Go at the moment. I think NABAS is a key reason that I got involved with this because we\'re bringing people together who are like-minded and the interaction that we create with these members and we also do with the do customers 13:38 as well it\'s phenomenal. When they start talking to people who are in the same predicament with the same issues you realize you\'re not isolated, pretty much every retailer and every decorator out there has the same issues. They will have the same problems how do I, where do I go, what do I do. And by bringing them together it\'s amazing how those problems can be solved. But my power of five is I always like to think that you should have five go-to people. You should always have these people that either your 14:06 relatives or your friends whatever. But five people who are experts in areas you are not an expert in and the people are willing to give hard and take and they\'re pretty hard to find. But when you find this right set of people it totally turns around your business. When you realize that there\'s someone else that really asks you back and it has good helpful advice that can help you grow it turns your business on its head.\r\n\r\n<strong>Interviewer:</strong> Okay, no George I think that\'s amazing advice and I think that the end message I\'d like to need to anyone of this listening is George is one of those people for you potentially. So Google George Go International or George NABAS Go International, George balloons Go International, any of those variations i\'ll also of course include the links. But George thank you so much and to everybody listening. See you next week.\r\n\r\n<strong>George:</strong