(274, 1, '2018-09-15 16:53:05', '2018-09-15 15:53:05', 'You can <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk\">buy balloons online</a> that come in all kinds of materials, sizes, and colours and, as we all know, no matter what occasion you are celebrating balloons are a great way to add a festive feel to the party space with ease. They are cheap, versatile and safe. What more could you ask for from party decorations?\r\n\r\nIf you buy balloons online - which will save you both time and money - you can even add a few extra touches of your own to make them extra special and give your balloon displays an extra personalized touch. Here are just a few ideas that are quick and easy to execute but can actually have a big impact on your party theme and decor overall.\r\n<h3>Smiling Balloon Buddies</h3>\r\nKids will love a smiling happy pal to take home with them after the party and it\'s easier than you might think to turn inexpensive balloons into fun friendly-faced balloons. All you have to do is inflate foil balloons and secure them with balloon tails (string or ribbon is just fine) and then use glue to attach little - or large - googly eyes, the kind you find in pound shops. From there all you need to do is add the mouths with a black - or red if the funny face balloon is going to be a bit glam - permanent marker and you\'re done!\r\n<h3>Geometric Stamped Balloons</h3>\r\nWant to add an arty, funky vibe to your party decor? It\'s easy. All you need are plain balloons in any colour, a few old makeup sponges and an inexpensive poster paint set. Simply cut up the sponges into squares, triangles, and dots, then use these \'sponge stamps to apply paint onto the inflated balloons in your favorite color, add some matching balloon tails, and voilà, you have something very funky and cool that\'s all your own!\r\n<h3>Temporary Tattoo Balloons</h3>\r\nDid you know that you can apply temporary tattoos to almost anything? That includes balloons and with just a few sheets of the kind of temporary tattoos that you can find everywhere, you can create a real ballon work of art. The tattoos can be applied to inflated balloons in the same way as they are to human skin - which means very easily - and with the right tattoo images, you can create some fabulous balloon works of art to match the theme of almost any kind of party with ease.', 'Simple Balloon Decoration Ideas to Personalize Your Party Decor', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'simple-balloon-decoration-ideas-to-personalize-your-party-decor', '', '', '2018-08-29 16:55:47', '2018-08-29 15:55:47', '', 0, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?p=274', 0, 'post', '', 0),
