(280, 1, '2018-09-30 17:05:07', '2018-09-30 16:05:07', 'Most of us have attended birthday parties for children that probably cost their parents a small fortune. While some parents have no problem forking out hundreds of pounds for expensive birthday supplies and entertainment, it is not necessary to spend over a hundred pounds to put together a birthday bash for your child that he or she will love.\r\n<h3>Go Self- Catering</h3>\r\nOne of the first ways you should consider to lower the cost of the party is by catering the party yourself. This can seem like a monumental task if the guest list is long, but asking friends and family members to lend a hand in the food preparation leading up to the party can make all the cooking and prep more manageable. There are also hundreds of easy recipes online that you can whip up the night before to cut back on party day stress that make use of very inexpensive ingredients, another big money saver.\r\n<h3>Go Party Supply Shopping Online</h3>\r\nCut the stress and expense of your kids birthday party by shopping for <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk\">cheap party supplies online</a>. You\'ll be surprised by just how much can be purchased via an online party supplies store and how affordable those supplies are when compared to the high cost of those high street party supplies stores.\r\n\r\nBuying cheap party supplies online is also a great way to pull off a themed party with ease. An online party supplies store will offer themed packs of party supplies, covering everything from the plates, cups and utensils to the favours for party bags to send the kids home with and even decorations to help theme the party space with ease. And don\'t forget the balloons! Kids love balloons and by shopping for cheap party supplies online you\'ll be able to find just the right ones to match the party\'s theme and save you some serious money.', 'Budgeting For Your Child\'s Birthday: How to Throw a Great Party for Under £100', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'budgeting-for-your-childs-birthday-how-to-throw-a-great-party-for-under-100', '', '', '2018-08-29 17:07:37', '2018-08-29 16:07:37', '', 0, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?p=280', 0, 'post', '', 0),
