(293, 1, '2018-11-29 01:44:20', '2018-11-29 01:44:20', 'Everyone loves <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Balloons\">party balloons</a> and they are the perfect addition to any party, no matter what the occasion. But you may not be aware of just how versatile modern party balloons are and the amazing party decor you can create by making use of them. Here are our top five ideas to provide you with some inspiration for your next party.\r\n<h2>Helium Balloon Photo Gallery</h2>\r\nNostalgic photos are a great addition to birthday parties, graduations, engagement parties,  or at any event where the progression of time - and how a person changes with it - is important. But why stick to photo albums or wall displays when you can attach photos to strings or streamers attached to helium balloons and use them to create an amazing floating photo gallery?\r\n<h2>Create Glowing Balloons</h2>\r\nHaving an outdoor evening party? Then you can use party balloons to create some wonderful glowing party decor with ease. Doing so is easy. Break and insert mini glow sticks into balloons before inflating them (helium-filled balloons are best) and then tie them to fences, decks and porches - or even trees - to provide a festive glow that will last all night long.\r\n<h2>Make Your New Year\'s Celebration More Exciting and Colorful with Confetti Stuffed Balloons</h2>\r\nHow do you celebrate when the clock strikes midnight on New Year\'s Eve? Champagne? party poppers? Why not switch things up this year and fill a giant balloon - some can be inflated to be up to be up to 3ft in diameter - with confetti to burst at midnight? It will create an exciting, colorful celebration to take you into the year to come and the cost to create this exciting display is less than a cheap bottle of wine.\r\n<h2>Dress Balloons in Tulle for an Elegant Decor Touch</h2>\r\nPrincess parties, weddings, engagement parties and more all call for a little more elegance and refinement in terms of party decor. One way to do that with ease is to \'dress up\' your party balloons.\r\n\r\nTulle is lightweight and elegant and comes in every colour of the rainbow, but it is also very lightweight. So lightweight that if it is used to wrap a helium-filled balloon it won\'t weigh it down. You can create decor that is even more stunning by adding ribbons or colourful, premade <a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Balloons\">balloon tails</a> as an extra finishing touch.\r\n<h2>Decorate a Cake</h2>\r\nNot gifted in the cake decoration department but need to budget buy a store bought cake? Add mini balloons! Simply inflate several in different colours and tie them to toothpicks and you can \'decorate\' a cake that looks truly stunning, without ever having to break out an icing tube!', 'Five Unusual Decor Uses For Party Balloons', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'five-unusual-decor-uses-for-party-balloons', '', '', '2018-11-14 08:03:54', '2018-11-14 08:03:54', '', 0, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?p=293', 0, 'post', '', 0),
