(310, 1, '2018-11-14 08:08:50', '2018-11-14 08:08:50', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you’re planning a party, there is a lot to consider. From picking out balloons to deciding what types of food to serve, it’s easy to feel overwhelmed.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One way to make the process easier is to pick a theme! </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let’s take a peek at some of the pieces you can use to create the perfect black and orange Halloween-themed party! </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Step #1: Decorate the party venue </span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bats are a key element of Halloween. These </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Decoration/Bat-Honeycomb-Hanging-Decoration?cPath=2_418_2436_2441&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bat Honeycomb Hanging Decorations</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> are a great way to add some spookiness to the party! You can hang them in several spots throughout the venue. They would also make a great photo prop for your guests! </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-179\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/BAT-DECOR.png\" alt=\"BAT DECORATION\" width=\"280\" height=\"342\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another hanging decoration idea is these </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Decoration/Black-Orange-Swirls-Decorations-30pk?cPath=2_418_2436_2441&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Orange &amp; Black Swirls Decorations</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. This set comes with a wide variety of 30 pieces. You can use these in every doorway and corner of the room! Like the previous item, they can also make excellent photo props! </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-180\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ORANGE-AND-BLACK-DECOR.png\" alt=\"ORANGE AND BLACK DECOR\" width=\"292\" height=\"288\" />\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Step #2: Ensure that your tableware is in line with the theme  </span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every great party has snacks or pizza. So you definitely need plates for your guests to load up on the food! Don’t use plain white plates, which will take away from your theme of black and orange. Use these </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Orange-Peel-Tableware/Orange-Peel-Paper-Plates-8pk?cPath=2_418_2436_2441&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Orange Paper Plates</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to impress your guests with your coordination skills! </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-181\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ORANGE-PLATE.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"289\" height=\"290\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition to plates, you will also need forks, spoons, and knives for your guests to use when they eat. Don’t let them be monsters and eat with their hands! Use this set of </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Jet-Black-Tableware/Jet-Black-Assorted-Cutlery-24pk?cPath=2_418_2436_2441&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Black Assorted Cutlery</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to give everyone the variety they need for your wide range of snack options! </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don’t leave out the napkins! Spills are bound to happen. While it’s important to keep the venue clean and tidy, you will want to opt for something to match your theme. These </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Jet-Black-Tableware/Jet-Black-2ply-Luncheon-Napkins-20pk?cPath=2_418_2436_2441&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jet Black Luncheon Napkins</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> are the perfect solution! </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Drinks are a necessary addition to every party. Halloween is a good time to make a spooky beverage! Think about making blood orange punch or adding gummy eyeballs to any type of drink. Use these </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Orange-Peel-Tableware/Orange-Peel-Paper-Cups-8pk?cPath=2_418_2436_2441&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Orange Paper Cups </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">to keep with the theme! </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Step 3: Don’t forget these! </span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can use these </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Black-Candy-Buffet/Black-Candy-Buffet-Popcorn-Treat-Boxes-x5?cPath=2_418_2436_2441&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Candy Popcorn Treat Boxes</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to give out party favors! Another idea is to make a candy buffet, where guests can fill a box with whatever candies they would like to take home with them!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-182\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/BLACK-AND-WHITE.png\" alt=\"BLACK AND WHITE POPCORN BOX\" width=\"268\" height=\"259\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you decide to go with the candy buffet idea, you will need a way to serve the different treats! You can use this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Orange-Peel-Candy-Buffet/Orange-Plastic-Scoop?cPath=2_418_2436_2441&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Orange Plastic Scoop</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for candy or for other snacks! It comes in both orange and </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Black-Candy-Buffet/Black-Plastic-Scoop\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">black</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> too. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-183\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ORANGE-SCOOP.png\" alt=\"ORANGE SCOOP\" width=\"267\" height=\"282\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, there you have it! How to throw the ultimate orange and black themed Halloween party in three steps!  </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Follow us on Twitter for party planning tips and to keep up to date with our latest product releases</span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gointuk\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">@gointuk</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">! </span>', 'How to Throw the Ultimate Orange & Black Themed Halloween Party!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '178-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-14 08:08:50', '2018-11-14 08:08:50', '', 178, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/178-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
