(313, 1, '2018-11-14 08:11:39', '2018-11-14 08:11:39', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When it comes to decorating for a Halloween party, it’s easy to forget about some of the most basic decorations, like balloons, streamers, and banners. We easily get caught up in baking creepy desserts or coming up with the scariest costumes. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So let’s take a look at some of the best Halloween balloons and get back to the basics! </span>\r\n<h2>1. Jack Faces Latex Balloons</h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Search no further than these </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Latex-Balloons/12-Jack-Faces-Quick-Link-Latex-Balloons-50pk\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jack Faces Balloons</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">! This package comes with 50, which means there are plenty to hang around the house, and you’ll have leftovers to give to the kids! </span>\r\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-145\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/1-1.png\" alt=\"pumpkin balloons\" width=\"307\" height=\"344\" />\r\n2. Happy Jacks Balloon Trio</h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This unique </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Supershape/3-Happy-Jacks-Supershape-Balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3 Happy Jacks Supershape Balloon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> will give your party an extra spark. It’s three balloons in one!</span>Foil Pumpkin Balloons\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-146\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/b.png\" alt=\"halloween balloons\" width=\"314\" height=\"323\" />\r\n<h2>3. Foil Pumpkin Balloons</h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Special-Events-And-Seasonal-Party-Supplies/Halloween/Halloween-Balloons/Halloween-Speciality/Pumpkin-Ultrashape-Foil-Balloons\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pumpkin Ultrashape Foil Balloons</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> are a good way to welcome guests to your party and would be nice hanging by the door! </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-147\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/c.png\" alt=\"foil pumpkin balloon \" width=\"319\" height=\"318\" />\r\n<h2><strong>4. Frankenstein Balloon</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He’s one of the most popular Halloween characters, and he will stand out at any bash! Hang this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Foil-Balloons/18-Frankenstein-Shape-Foil-Balloons\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Frankenstein Shaped Foil Balloon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to get your guests into the Halloween spirit! </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-148\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"306\" height=\"369\" />\r\n<h2><strong>5. Day of the Dead Balloon</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Want to add a more original idea of Halloween to your party? Go back to the roots of the holiday and use this Day of the </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foils/18-inch-Day-Of-The-Dead-halloween-helium-foil-balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dead Halloween Foil Balloon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">! </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-149\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/e.png\" alt=\"Day of the Dead Balloon \" width=\"314\" height=\"323\" />\r\n<h2><strong>6. Spider Eyes Balloons</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These creepy balloons will give your guests the jitters. The </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-18-Inch-Foils/18-inch-Day-Of-The-Dead-halloween-helium-foil-balloon\"