(314, 1, '2018-11-14 08:12:10', '2018-11-14 08:12:10', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you’re coming up with costume ideas, it’s hard enough to decide what you want to dress up as, let alone find all of the necessary pieces without breaking the bank. </span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Today we’re going to share 12 of the spookiest masks with you, so you can get started on your Halloween costume! </span>\n<h2><strong>1. Hockey Masks</strong></h2>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">  These </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Masks/Hockey-Masks\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hockey Masks</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> are an easy way to start out any creepy costume. There’s just something eerie about them…</span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-130\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/1.png\" alt=\"halloween mask\" width=\"448\" height=\"448\" />\n<h2><strong>2. Chucky Mask</strong></h2>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Looking for a classic thriller costume? Look no further than this</span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Masks/Officially-Licensed-Chucky-Latex-Overhead-Mask\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Latex Chucky Mask</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">!  </span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-131\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/2.png\" alt=\"chucky mask\" width=\"404\" height=\"416\" />\n\n&nbsp;\n<h2><strong>3. Hell Boy Mask </strong></h2>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Masks/Officially-Licensed-Latex-Hell-Boy-Mask\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Latex Hell Boy Mask </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is easy to pair with other creepy clothing to create the perfect Hell Boy costume on a time crunch! </span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-132\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/3.png\" alt=\"Hellboy mask\" width=\"427\" height=\"404\" />\n<h2><strong>4. Evil Clown Mask </strong></h2>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For those who are afraid of clowns, this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers/Evil-Clown-Masks\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Evil Clown Mask</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is particularly creepy! It’s sure to freak out a few of your friends. </span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/4.png\" alt=\"clown mask\" width=\"410\" height=\"422\" />\n<h2><strong>5. White Rabbit Mask </strong></h2>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How can something that seems so innocent and sweet suddenly be crazy scary? This </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Fancy-Dress-Costumes/Halloween-Fancy-Dress/Halloween-Masks/White-Rabbit-Mask?cPath=2_418_1126&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">White Rabbit Mask </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is no child’s toy! </span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-134\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/5.png\" alt=\"rabbit mask\" width=\"439\" height=\"421\" />\n<h2><strong>6. Sinister Skeleton Mask</strong></h2>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Skeletons are creepy anyway, but this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers/Sinister-Skeleton-Masks\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sinister Skeleton Mask</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> will take your costume one step further! </span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-135\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/6.png\" alt=\"skeleton mask\" width=\"441\" height=\"442\" />\n<h2><strong>7. Blood Splatter Skull Mask</strong></h2>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How can we make the previous mask just a little scarier? Add blood to make things a bit gorier, and you’ll get this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Fancy-Dress-Costumes/Halloween-Fancy-Dress/Halloween-Masks/Blood-Splatter-Skull-Mask?cPath=2_418_1126&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Blood Splatter Skull Mask</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">!</span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-136\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/7.png\" alt=\"halloween mask\" width=\"410\" height=\"437\" />\n\n&nbsp;\n<h2><strong>8. Skull Mask</strong></h2>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We’re going back to the basics with this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Fancy-Dress-Costumes/Halloween-Fancy-Dress/Halloween-Masks/Blood-Splatter-Skull-Mask?cPath=2_418_1126&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Skull Mask</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, which gives you lots of options to elaborate on the rest of your getup! It also looks creepy by itself, so you don’t have to commit to a full costume if that isn’t your thing.</span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-137\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/8.png\" alt=\"skull mask\" width=\"435\" height=\"429\" />\n<h1><strong>9. Decaying Zombie Mask</strong></h1>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This</span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Masks/Decaying-Zombie-Mask?cPath=2_418_1126&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Decaying Zombie Mask</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> will frighten anyone you come close to, and we can see why! It would also be a good one to protect you in case of an apocalypse. </span>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-138\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/9.png\" alt=\"zombie mask\" width=\"426\" height=\"421\" />\n<h1><strong>10. 3 Face Mask </strong></h1>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\