(316, 1, '2018-11-14 08:15:26', '2018-11-14 08:15:26', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Halloween is just around the corner. That means it’s time to start planning some spooktacular parties that will send shivers down your guest’s spines!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Need some inspiration? </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Luckily for you, we have put together a list of 5 things to make your party </span><b>extra </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">spooky:</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#1 Monster Lab Halloween Labels</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Liven up your drinks table, by removing the original labels from your soda bottles, and replacing them with these colourful </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Monster-Lab-Halloween-Bottle-Labels-x4\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Monster Lab</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> labels. Don’t forget to stock up on Halloween themed</span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Themed/Witches-Crew-Paper-Cups-8ct\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> disposable cups</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-88\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/labels.png\" alt=\"halloween labels\" width=\"434\" height=\"456\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Top tips:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Use different coloured beverages for each label to make it seem even more realistic!</span>&nbsp;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Make some gummy spider ice cubes! To make these, take a clean ice tray, and place a small gummy spider in each compartment. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Then fill the tray with water as normal and place it in the freezer for 4 hours to set. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Remove the ice cubes from the freezer and place them in a serving bowl so that your guests can help themselves!  </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#2 Spooky Eye Cello Bags</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What better way to bid your guests farewell than by handing out treat bags? Our </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers/Spooky-Eyes-Cello-Bags-20ct\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">spooky eye cello bags</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> will do just the trick! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They are the perfect size to be filled with several goodies!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-89\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/party-bags.png\" alt=\"party bags\" width=\"217\" height=\"550\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Top tips: </b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you are stuck for ideas on what to put inside the treat bags, you can’t go wrong with sweets! </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For more treat bag ideas, check out our </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Accessories?sort=20a&amp;page=2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Halloween accessories!</span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#3 Pumpkin LED Lighting Garland</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To create an extra spooky atmosphere, why not dim the lights and hang this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Pumpkin-LED-Light-Garland\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">LED pumpkin lighting garland</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> around the room? </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alternatively, you could arrange these lights on your buffet table. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-90\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/pumpkindgarland.png\" alt=\"pumpkindgarland\" width=\"446\" height=\"459\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Tip top:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Catch your guests off guard by placing gruesome items around the room. For example, you could place a</span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Essentials/Severed-Life-Like-Foot?cPath=&amp;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> life - like severed foot </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">at the back of the room, where unsuspecting guests will discover them. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#4 Inflatable Coffin Buffet</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fill this </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers/Inflatable-Coffin-Buffet\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">inflatable coffin buffet</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> up with ice and load it up with all of your drinks, then allow your guests to help themselves. This is a spooky, but fun way to display your beverages!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-91\" src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/inflatablecoffin.png\" alt=\"inflatablecoffin\" width=\"342\" height=\"548\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Top tips:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Place a few of these flickering </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers/Flickering-Skull-And-Pumpkins-12pk\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">glitter skull and pumpkin</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ornaments in and around the coffin. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For drinks that you will be serving from a punch bowl, garnish the edge of the bowl with some gummy worms! </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">#5 Sparkle Spooky Balloon</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Balloons are an </span><b>effective </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and </span><b>inexpensive</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> way to decorate your party rooms. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We have a wide range of Halloween themed balloons - this one is perfect for your spooky Halloween party! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s our </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Foil-Balloons/18-Sparkle-Spooky-Halloween-Foil-Balloon\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">sparkle spooky balloon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and it will go well with the flickering, glittery skulls and pumpkins! </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Conclusion</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So folks, there you have it, 5 items that can add extra spookiness to your Halloween party! </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can also find more spooky </span><a href=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/Halloween-Special-Offers\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">special offer items</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> on our website. Our unique selection gives you many options that will make your party planning much easier! </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Follow us on Twitter for party planning tips and to keep up to date with our latest product releases </span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gointuk\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">@gointuk</span></a>', '5 Items That Will Make Your Halloween Party Extra Spooky', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '86-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-14 08:15:26', '2018-11-14 08:15:26', '', 86, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/86-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', ''