 customized balloons.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Logos, headlines, icons, and mascots, can be printed on\nGrabo inflatable balloons. With no limitations on shapes and colours, the image\nof your company will float freely in the air, in shopping centres, inside their\ncompany or anywhere you want to.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For many years they have been offering our products to\nmultinational companies, advertising agencies and private customers for events,\nceremonies, and celebrations of all kinds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In addition to the standard sizes, available in more than\n1.000 variations, they have balloons in Supershape (from 50 cm to 1,10 m),\nMinishape (aprox. 35-40 cm) and Shake (with handle, aprox. 60-70 cm) format.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Balloons are available with metallic, transparent, standard\nand glittered holographic material.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The orders are subject to a tolerance percentage on the\nquantity of 10%, more or less.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are looking for a Balloon Wholesaler stocking Grabo Balloons, look no further than <a href=\"http://www.gointernational.co.uk\">GO International</a>, The UK’s leading Importer and Party Wholesaler. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>GO International. Unit 15, The io Centre, Arlington Business Park, Stevenage. SG1 2BD. Tel: 01438 745746<br><a href=\"http://www.gointernational.co.uk \">www.gointernational.co.uk </a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wholesale Balloons Wholesale Party Supplies. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Grabo Balloons From Your Leading Balloon Wholesaler.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '359-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-10-17 17:11:53', '2019-10-17 16:11:53', '', 359, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/359-revis