nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; GRAD</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; CONGRATS</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; THANK YOU</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SPECIAL\nMESSAGE</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; NON\nMESSAGE</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SPANISH</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; FALL\n&amp; WINTER</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SOLID\nCOLORS</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ALPHABET\n&amp; NUMBERS</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; PET\nWALKERS</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SHAPES</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[362,363,364]} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Grabo-rainbow-gem-balloon-gr74002.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"362\" data-link=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?attachment_id=362\" class=\"wp-image-362\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Grabo-rainbow-grabo-globe-gr74001.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"363\" data-link=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?attachment_id=363\" class=\"wp-image-363\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Grabo-rainbow-square-balloon-gr74003.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"364\" data-link=\"https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/?attachment_id=364\" class=\"wp-image-364\"/></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Currently Grabo has more than 10.000 square meters of\nproduction space, 5 separate units, over 30 machines involved in the production\nwhich makes it not only the biggest manufacturer in Europe, but also the one\nwith broadest capacity for continued growth</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But it is not just about that. There’s a &nbsp;mix and match experience with hunger, having\ninvested in newcomers in their twenties and brought them along to develop\ntogether with the seniors of the business, they have more than 20 artists\nensuring that every year they keep on track with the best trends and develop\nthe most refined and edgy balloons, 5 engineers constantly developing new\nshapes and new materials to push forward our edge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In 2011 Grabo went on to complete its growth path: It\ndoubled its spaces and created a personnel friendly environment, transforming a\nproduction premise into a home and community for the affiliated, with saunas,\nfootball pitches, beach-volley grounds, sun-beds, party-gazebos and a vegetable\ngarden open to all.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CUSTOM WHOLESALE BALLOONS</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For companies • Events</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For over 30 years they have been producing personalised\nballoons of all shapes and sizes, for companies all over the world and events\nof any kind. Their artisanal procedure and the great assortment of colours and\nmaterials enable a wide versatility of customized balloons.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Logos, headlines, icons, and mascots, can be printed on\nGrabo inflatable balloons. With no limitations on shapes and colours, the image\nof your company will float freely in the air, in shopping centres, inside their\ncompany or anywhere you want to.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For many years they have been offering our products to\nmultinational companies, advertising agencies and private customers for events,\nceremonies, and celebrations of all kinds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In addition to the standard sizes, available in more than\n1.000 variations, they have balloons in Supershape (from 50 cm to 1,10 m),\nMinishape (aprox. 35-40 cm) and Shake (with handle, aprox. 60-70 cm) format.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Balloons are available with metallic, transparent, standard\nand glittered holographic material.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The orders are subject to a tolerance percentage on the\nquantity of 10%, more or less.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are looking for a Balloon Wholesaler stocking Grabo Balloons, look no further than <a href=\"http://www.gointernational.co.uk\">GO International</a>, The UK’s leading Importer and Party Wholesaler. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>GO International. Unit 15, The io Centre, Arlington Business Park, Stevenage. SG1 2BD. Tel: 01438 745746<br><a href=\"http://www.gointernational.co.uk \">www.gointernational.co.uk </a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wholesale Balloons Wholesale Party Supplies. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Grabo Balloons From Your Leading Balloon Wholesaler.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '359-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-10-17 17:20:15', '2019-10-17 16:20:15', '', 359, 'https://www.gointernational.co.uk/blog/359-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
